<title>THE GOSPEL</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chanchin Pha thu gi chuh ngai un,
 Krista'n thing ah A thuok tai;
 Zahngaihna lui chuh a pung tai,
 Hehpihna'n a luong zak tai,
 Migilo, liengvai, (3) nang dinga thi chuh en in. (2)

[V2]
 2. Aw zie tang achun va chieh in,
 Tuni'n hinna chuh mu'n la;
 Krista'n A hun chiel hi lui ah,
 Na gitloh cheng sawp thieng di'n,
 Uoi-ai-ki'n la nang, (3) aphat laiin hung mai in. (2)

[V3]
 3. Hehpihna lui a luong zing hi,
 Sang tam takin a chang tau;
 Tuhin le a thak bang ahi,
 Hukdampa naka put chuh,
 Beimang ki'n la aw, (3) nang di'n Krista a thi tai. (2)

[V4]
 4. Krista chuh I lawi hung hin tin,
 Van akhun kituok hitiu;
 Chun van tuipi a kisil in,
 Ei Tanpa lungsietna ah,
 A hauhsakna leh (3) A lal zie chuh mu tai tiu. (2)</lyrics>
</song>